item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Item_Category_Question_Answer Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Container_Product_Item_Category_Question_Answer data type represents an answer to an item category question. It contains the category, the question being answered, and the answer. Local answer The answer to the question. Type: string categoryCode The product item category code. Type: string categoryId The product item category id. Type: integer questionId The product item category question id.
